track.name: The Less I Know the Better

wiki.summary: "The Less I Know the Better" is a song by Australian psychedelic rock act Tame Impala. It was released on 29 November 2015 as the third single from his third studio album "Currents". The song's accompanying music video takes place in a high school, where a basketball player suffers a broken heart. The song peaked at number 23 on the Belgian Flanders singles chart, number 66 on the ARIA Singles Chart and number 195 on the French Singles Chart. In the U.S., the song charted at number 36 on Billboard's Hot Rock Songs chart. Read more on Last.fm.
